                              Release Information

A brand new hit from the creators of Gardenscapes: A talented young writer, 
Scarlett, decides to buy a beautiful 19th century mansion away from the hustle 
and bustle of the big city hoping to find her lost inspiration. Little does 
she know that the new home needs some serious renovation. You can help Scarlett 
restore it and bring inspiration back to her life! Look for the old things 
tucked away in the house, conduct sales and turn a ramshackle building into a 
cozy palace! But remember: The mansion is full of secrets of its previous 
dwellers. Unraveled, they will help Scarlett write her best novel yet!
